Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:01.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,《少年谢尔顿》前情提要\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Previously on Young Sheldon...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.78,0:00:04.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-安珀是谁  -我在交往的女生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Who is Amber? - A girl I'm seeing.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.17,0:00:05.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,曼蒂知道吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Does Mandy know?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.33,0:00:06.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是她让我去的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It was actually her idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.97,0:00:08.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的约会进行得如何\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How was your date?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.99,0:00:10.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实我们分手了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We broke up.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.69,0:00:11.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发生什么了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.89,0:00:13.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么  我就是想来这里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I just wanted to be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.31,0:00:15.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们也想你来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's what we wanted, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.88,0:00:18.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还能送我别的生日礼物\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There's something else you could do for my birthday.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.19,0:00:20.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我两周前才刚生完小孩  不行\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I had a baby two weeks ago, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.96,0:00:21.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是指那个啦\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Not that.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.85,0:00:23.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是指什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Then what?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.65,0:00:25.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嫁给我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Marry me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.86,0:00:32.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.32,0:00:36.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么鬼\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.82,0:00:39.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-你愿意嫁给...  -我有听到你的问题\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Will you marry... - Yeah, I heard the question.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.15,0:00:40.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你为什么要问这个\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Why are you asking it?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.49,0:00:43.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我爱你啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, 'cause I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.75,0:00:44.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你有吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Do ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.78,0:00:46.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.74,0:00:48.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你刚刚还跟另一个女生在约会\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You were just on a date with another girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.17,0:00:50.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对啊  我现在本可以在她家呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah, and I could be at her place right now,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.95,0:00:52.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我却在你身旁\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but instead, I'm here with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.23,0:00:54.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是谢谢你的牺牲啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, well, thank you for your sacrifice.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.54,0:00:56.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一个18岁小伙  你相信我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm 18 years old-- believe me,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.28,0:00:57.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这绝对是重大牺牲\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}that's a sacrifice.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.21,0:01:00.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这下好了  你满意了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, great. Are you happy?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.00,0:01:03.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她哭或许是因为她妈妈\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Maybe she's crying because her mom
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.19,0:01:04.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不愿意嫁给她爸爸\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}don't want to marry her dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.83,0:01:05.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她在哭也有可能是因为\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Or maybe she's crying
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.58,0:01:07.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她妈妈想勒死她爸爸\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}'cause her mom wants to strangle her dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.01,0:01:09.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你来啦  生日男孩\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hey there, birthday boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.65,0:01:11.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么这么早就回家了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What're you doing home so early?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.44,0:01:13.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,貌似是回来浪费时间了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Apparently, wasting my time.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.04,0:01:16.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不可以说来就来  说求婚就求婚啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You cannot just show up here and spring a proposal on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.29,0:01:17.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你求婚啦\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You proposed?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.05,0:01:20.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用担心  不会有下次了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Don't worry. It won't happen again.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.07,0:01:28.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,婚礼选哪天呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So, when's the wedding?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.59,0:01:54.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在干嘛呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.96,0:01:56.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸跟我在看《星际旅行》\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Dad and I are watching Star Trek.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.67,0:02:00.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来是我独自在看《星际旅行》\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I guess I'm watching Star Trek.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.87,0:02:02.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想我陪你一起看吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Want me to watch with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.02,0:02:03.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然  我给你前情提要一下\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sure. Let me catch you up.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.98,0:02:07.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,进取号航行到埃米尼尔七星\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The Enterprise is traveling to Eminiar VII
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.14,0:02:09.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想解决他们与邻星维迪卡之间的战争\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}to resolve their war with the neighboring Vendikar.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.69,0:02:12.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但柯克怀疑双方并不是在真正打仗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But Kirk suspects that instead of having a real war,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.91,0:02:14.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,埃米尼尔与维迪卡之间\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}the Eminiaries and the Vendikaries
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.56,0:02:17.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是很认真地在打计算机模拟战争\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}are having a computer-simulated conflict.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.07,0:02:18.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,柯克认为\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}In Kirk's opinion,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.78,0:02:20.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么做反而减弱了对战争的恐惧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}by keeping the horrors of war at arm's length,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.74,0:02:22.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,使得战争绵延不绝\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}they're simply prolonging it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.22,0:02:24.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我问你个问题\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Let me ask you something.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.73,0:02:26.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就是解答达人  你问吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Answers are my thing. Go for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.69,0:02:30.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真的相信这些宇宙外星人之类的东西吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Do you really believe in all this space alien stuff?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.19,0:02:31.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这只是很简单的概率问题啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, it's simple probability theory.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.97,0:02:33.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在我们这个星系里就有上千亿颗星球\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There are over a hundred billion stars in our galaxy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.99,0:02:36.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有个几颗能支持生命存在的星球几率不小吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So it's likely that a few of them could support life,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.14,0:02:38.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,甚至可能是有科技的文明\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}or even technological civilization.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.11,0:02:41.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,耶稣也为了它们的罪而死吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And did Jesus die for their sins as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.01,0:02:43.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你有你相信的故事  我也有我的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You have your stories, I have mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.57,0:02:47.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小乔治好像到家了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Whew. Sounds like Georgie's home.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.73,0:02:49.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乔治  醒醒\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}George, wake up.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.29,0:02:51.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好陪你儿子看《星际旅行》\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Watch Star Trek with your son.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.45,0:02:56.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,演到哪了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What's happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.61,0:02:58.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,进取号航行到埃米尼尔七星\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, the Enterprise is traveling to Eminiar VII
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.99,0:03:00.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想解决他们与邻星维迪卡之间的战争\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}to resolve their war with the neighboring Vendikar.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.79,0:03:04.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但柯克怀疑双方并不是在真正打仗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}However, Kirk suspects that instead of fighting a real war,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.17,0:03:05.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,埃米尼尔与维迪卡之间\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}the Eminiaries and the Vendikaries
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.39,0:03:07.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是很认真地在打计算机模拟战争\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}are fighting a computer-simulated conflict.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.22,0:03:09.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-不许睡  醒醒  -我醒着呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Uh-uh. Stay awake. - I'm awake.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.70,0:03:11.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-小乔治  -干嘛\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Georgie? - what?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.22,0:03:18.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就想来祝你生日快乐\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I just want to wish you a happy birthday.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.36,0:03:20.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.93,0:03:22.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你没事吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Everything okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.60,0:03:24.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不想聊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't want to talk about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.10,0:03:27.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你跟安珀吵架了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You and Amber have a fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.18,0:03:30.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们分手了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We broke up.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.53,0:03:32.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.14,0:03:33.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心疼你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.19,0:03:40.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或许也不是坏事  你与曼蒂还有丝丝\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Maybe it's a good thing because you and Mandy and CeeCee
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.15,0:03:42.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是个多么有爱的小家庭啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}make such a cute little family.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.06,0:03:45.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,告诉你  我有注意到她看你的眼神\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You know, I see the way she's been looking at you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.41,0:03:46.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-别说了  -我是说真的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Stop. - I mean it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.82,0:03:49.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得她已经准备好再给你一次机会\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I think she's ready to give you another chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.17,0:03:52.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊  或许我应该向她求婚\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah, maybe I should just ask her to marry me.
