Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.26,0:04:08.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小乔治通常早上会过来喂她\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Georgie usually comes over and feeds her in the morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.97,0:04:10.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但他好像在生我气\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But I think he's mad at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.32,0:04:13.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊  当你拒绝男人的求婚\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah, you reject a guy's marriage proposal,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.19,0:04:16.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们很容易走心\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}they tend to take it personal.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.07,0:04:18.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这是经验之谈吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You speaking from experience?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.46,0:04:21.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老娘当年也让不少人心碎过\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I've broken a couple of hearts in my day.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.26,0:04:27.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他太突然  我只是有一点吓到\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He just caught me off guard. That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.55,0:04:29.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在你有时间好好想了  你怎么觉得\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And now that you've had time, what do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.94,0:04:31.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么只能这么极端\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Why does it have to be all or nothing?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.74,0:04:34.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我能理解他不爽我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I get that he's mad at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.98,0:04:37.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我没想到他会就这么不来喂自己闺女\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I just didn't think he'd stop showing up for his daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.67,0:04:40.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让他冷静过后他就会想通\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, he'll come around. He just needs to cool off.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.31,0:04:46.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我问问看  妈妈\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Let me ask. Mom,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.40,0:04:48.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我这周六可以去看电影吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}can I go to the movies on Saturday?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.68,0:04:49.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.95,0:04:51.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她答应了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She said yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.09,0:04:52.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的  那就这么约啦\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Okay, it's a date.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.71,0:04:56.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Who was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.73,0:04:58.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,布兰妮·珀金斯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Britney Perkins.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.96,0:05:02.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她是那个头箍牙套小胖妹吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She that, uh, chunky one with the headgear?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.45,0:05:06.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是  她是啦啦队的  而且还有一口好牙\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No, she's a cheerleader and her teeth are beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.17,0:05:10.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后她...  约你出去吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And... and she asked you out.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.00,0:05:15.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你对布兰妮·珀金斯有何认识\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What do you know about Britney Perkins?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.17,0:05:18.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个就是她\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's her right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.87,0:05:21.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她很可爱\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She's cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.98,0:05:24.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这还是她长胸之前呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And this was before her boobs came in.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.67,0:05:26.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以她在耍比利\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So, she's just messing with Billy?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.27,0:05:28.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她也有可能是真的约他啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She might've asked him out.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.85,0:05:31.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好啦  她在耍他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Okay, she's messing with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.60,0:05:33.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你跟这个女生是朋友吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You friends with this girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.27,0:05:35.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我倒想呢  她可超受欢迎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I wish. She is so popular.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.27,0:05:37.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有一次她说喜欢我穿的那件衣服\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}One time she said she liked my outfit--
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.98,0:05:39.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我穿了整整一周\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I wore it for a week.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.93,0:05:42.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我该怎么办\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What am I gonna do?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.80,0:05:47.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可以跟比利说他还太小  不可以约会\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You could tell Billy he's too young to date.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.36,0:05:51.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这招好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.68,0:05:55.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你很可能是你家最酷的那个人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You might be the coolest person in this house.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.67,0:05:57.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,未免太容易  但还是谢谢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Low bar, but thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.87,0:06:00.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,林克莱特博士  我需要跟你谈谈\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Dr. Linkletter, I need to talk to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.68,0:06:02.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们在我办公室了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Are we in my office?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.89,0:06:03.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不在\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.55,0:06:05.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那现在就不是我的办公时间\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Then these are not my office hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.16,0:06:08.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是利用我对时间表的尊重来治我吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Are you using my love of schedules against me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.05,0:06:09.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.42,0:06:10.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高招\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well done.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.95,0:06:24.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-林克莱特博士  我需要跟你聊聊  -真棒啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Dr. Linkletter, I need to talk to you. - Great.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.36,0:06:26.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你有门路让我能进望远镜观测室吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Do you think you could get me access to the telescope room?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.70,0:06:29.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想寻找能够支持生命存在的星球\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I want to search for exoplanets that could support life.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.28,0:06:30.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想家了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Are you feeling homesick?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.62,0:06:34.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-你是在暗指我来自外星球吗  -没错\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Are you implying that I'm from another planet? - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.27,0:06:35.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我接受你的夸奖\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Compliment accepted.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.25,0:06:36.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说回望远镜观测室\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Now, about the telescope room,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.96,0:06:38.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看《星际旅行》的时候想到...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I was watching Star Trek and it got me thinking...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.78,0:06:40.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢尔顿  尝试寻找\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sheldon, searching for life
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.28,0:06:42.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其他星球上的生命不是什么正经科学\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}on other planets isn't serious science.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.46,0:06:44.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把这种事留给阴谋论大军干吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Leave that to the tinfoil hat brigade.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.66,0:06:47.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但从统计学角度来看  有那么多恒星与行星\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But statistically, given the number of stars and planets,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.01,0:06:49.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们很有希望找到一个能支持生命存在的星球\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}it's likely we could find one capable of supporting life.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.30,0:06:50.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果真被我们找到  那将会是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And if we did, it would be the greatest
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.41,0:06:52.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,科学史上最伟大的发现\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}scientific discovery of all time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.13,0:06:53.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我也往头上戴水果帽\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yes, and if I had fruit on my head,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.43,0:06:54.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也能成为卡门·米兰达呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'd be Carmen Miranda.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.02,0:06:56.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不太懂你这个哏\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm not familiar with that reference.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.56,0:06:59.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以在电影中戴着水果帽歌舞闻名的女星\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She sang and danced with fruit on her head.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.02,0:07:00.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她为什么头上要戴水果啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Why would she have fruit on her head?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.32,0:07:02.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我哪知道  为防自己肚子饿吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't know, in case she got hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.14,0:07:03.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别做梦了  谢尔顿\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's not gonna happen, Sheldon!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.61,0:07:05.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么能直接无视一个调查方向\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How can you just dismiss a line of inquiry out of hand?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.98,0:07:08.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢尔顿  我有时会为了爽而拒绝人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sheldon, sometimes I say no just for kicks.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.85,0:07:10.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但这次是为了你好而拒绝\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This time it's for your own good.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.19,0:07:13.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所有追寻小绿人的科学家  都成为了笑柄\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Scientists who pursue little green men get laughed at.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.46,0:07:15.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在乎的是科学  而不是我个人名誉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, I care about science, not my reputation.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.39,0:07:16.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你不愿意帮我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And if you're not willing to help me,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.38,0:07:17.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我知道还有谁能帮我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I know someone who is.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.02,0:07:21.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们会被物理学家\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We'll be mocked by physicists,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.04,0:07:24.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,工程师  甚至数学家们嘲笑的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}engineers, even mathematicians.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.04,0:07:26.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们不会光说你是个傻逼\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And they don't just say you're an idiot--
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.76,0:07:27.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们还会证明\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}they prove it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.93,0:07:30.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我头上有水果  我还能变成卡门·米兰达呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And if I had fruit on my head, I'd be Carmen Miranda.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.44,0:07:32.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.56,0:07:33.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也没懂这个哏\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I didn't understand it either.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.13,0:07:40.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-早  -早\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Hey. - Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.52,0:07:43.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-你还好吗  -不好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Are you okay? - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.24,0:07:45.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,布兰妮·珀金斯约我去看电影\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Britney Perkins asked me to go to the movies,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.36,0:07:46.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我妈妈不准我去约会\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but my mom says I'm not allowed to date
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.74,0:07:48.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我年纪还太小\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}because I'm too young.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.44,0:07:50.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我相信她只是担心你啦\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm sure she's just looking out for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.11,0:07:54.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或许我可以偷溜出门去找她\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Maybe I could sneak out and still go with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.45,0:07:55.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别这么做\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Don't do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.76,0:07:57.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也偷溜出自己家啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You sneak out of your house.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.47,0:07:59.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是问题儿童  但你又不是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Because I'm a troubled kid. You're not.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.23,0:08:02.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但这是第一次有女生来约我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But this is the first time a girl's ever asked me out.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.33,0:08:07.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比利  她并没有喜欢你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Billy, she doesn't like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.58,0:08:08.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这话什么意思\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.54,0:08:10.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她这周六要在家里办派对\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She's having a party at her house on Saturday.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.84,0:08:12.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她不会去看电影的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She's not going to the movies.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.07,0:08:14.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是在整你罢了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's a prank.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.94,0:08:20.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-别难过  -没关系啦\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- I'm sorry. - It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.16,0:08:23.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可以陪你去看电影啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'll go to the movies with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.86,0:08:25.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不用这样啦\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You don't have to do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.13,0:08:26.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我愿意啊  会很好玩吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I want to. It'll be fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.45,0:08:29.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你不去她的派对了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But aren't you going to her party?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.22,0:08:30.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她也没邀请我啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I wasn't invited.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.62,0:08:32.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但这又如何呢  她就是个贱人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Which is fine, 'cause she's a bitch.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.02,0:08:35.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还真是个问题少女呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Wow. You are troubled.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.18,0:08:42.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈格迈尔校长  我们有个问题\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}President Hagemeyer, we have a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.15,0:08:44.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又怎么了  谢尔顿\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What now, Sheldon?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.18,0:08:46.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,贩卖机里的巧克力饮料不够冰吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The Yoo-hoos in the vending machine aren't cold enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.85,0:08:47.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还真的不够冰\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Actually, they aren't,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.68,0:08:48.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但这件事稍后再说\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but we'll table that for later.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.92,0:08:51.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想要使用天文望远镜的许可来搜索系外行星  \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I need telescope time to search for exoplanets,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.22,0:08:54.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,林克莱特博士与斯特吉斯博士都拒绝了我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and Dr. Linkletter and Dr. Sturgis have denied my request.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.08,0:08:55.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-为什么  -他们说这种研究\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Why? - They said that kind of research
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.77,0:08:58.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只会给我和学校招致非议\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}would expose both me and the university to criticism.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.53,0:09:00.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么可能呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, that's outrageous.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.47,0:09:01.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你允许我使用吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So, you'll give me access?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.95,0:09:04.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然不行  我也想  但是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Gosh, no. I want to, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.21,0:09:05.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是区区校长\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm just the president.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.51,0:09:11.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,使用望远镜必须得到科学顾问的批准\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Use of the telescope has to be approved by a science advisor.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.87,0:09:12.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真有其事吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Is that true?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.01,0:09:14.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听起来像真事吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Does it sound true?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.30,0:09:16.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-像吧  -那就是真有其事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- I suppose it does. - Then I suppose it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.36,0:09:18.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我干嘛浪费时间来找你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Why did I even come to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.05,0:09:20.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以下次记得别来了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Remember that next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.55,0:09:28.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,提醒一下  她今天要打针\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Just a warning, she's gonna get some shots today.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.11,0:09:30.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听着  宝宝\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Okay, kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.41,0:09:32.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不哭  妈妈就不哭\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You don't cry, I don't cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.46,0:09:34.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实妈妈无论如何都会哭的  但你别哭哦\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Actually, I'm gonna cry either way, but you don't cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.89,0:09:36.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我来了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.57,0:09:38.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我都不确定你会来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Wasn't sure you were coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.32,0:09:40.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我这不是来了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, I'm here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.23,0:09:41.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就是麦卡利斯特先生吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You must be Mr. McAllister.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.83,0:09:44.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-是她姓麦卡利斯特  我姓库珀  -别闹行吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- She's McAllister. I'm Cooper. - Can you not?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.33,0:09:46.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是生怕她误会我们是夫妻啦\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, I just don't want her to think we're married.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.29,0:09:47.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道那会让你觉得很丢人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I know how embarrassing that'd be for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.90,0:09:49.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没这么说\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That is not what I said.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.33,0:09:51.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们没结婚\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We're not married.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.32,0:09:52.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不关我的事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Really not my business.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.50,0:09:53.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说不定与你有关\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It might be.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.14,0:09:55.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是儿科医生  他像小孩一样在耍幼稚\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're a pediatrician, he's being a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.53,0:09:57.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想我们成为一家人怎么就是耍幼稚了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How does wanting us to be a family make me a child?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.89,0:09:59.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真想在陌生人面前吵架吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You really want to have this fight in front of a stranger?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.91,0:10:02.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已婚人士总是吵个不停啊  不是吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Married people fight all the time, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.60,0:10:04.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不用回答这个问题\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Uh... You don't have to answer that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.14,0:10:05.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们并没有\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And no, they don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.61,0:10:07.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-其实...  -老娘不是叫你别回答吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Actually... - I said don't answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.50,0:10:13.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈尔迈尔校长愿意力挺我是很好啦\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}While it was nice to have President Hagemeyer on my side,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.33,0:10:16.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我仍需要顾问的批准才能进行研究\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I still needed to find an advisor to approve my research.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.84,0:10:19.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一个英勇无畏者\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Some intrepid soul who was unafraid of
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.16,0:10:21.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无惧声誉受损  敢于给予睿智之人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}tarnishing their reputation by taking a chance
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.56,0:10:24.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和未经证实的理论机会\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}on a brilliant mind and a bold, untested idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.80,0:10:28.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.14,0:10:30.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,系外行星\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Exoplanets?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.38,0:10:33.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开什么玩笑\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Nah...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.46,0:10:34.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没门\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.52,0:10:37.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-埃文斯博士  我想...  -不行\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Dr. Evans, I have... - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.02,0:10:41.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,经历了八次拒绝  三次捧腹大笑\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Eight noes, three belly laughs,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.88,0:10:44.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和一位教授假装不会说英语之后\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and one professor who pretended not to speak English later,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.90,0:10:46.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我终于找到了那个人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I found my man.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.42,0:10:47.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打扰了  普拉卡什博士\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Excuse me, Dr. Prakash?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.74,0:10:49.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-我是谢尔顿·库珀  -是你啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- I'm Sheldon Cooper. - Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.46,0:10:50.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我听说过你很多事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I've heard a lot about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.91,0:10:52.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我从没听过你的事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And I've heard nothing about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.41,0:10:54.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,普拉卡什博士  我在寻找一位导师\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Dr. Prakash, I'm on the hunt for a mentor
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.34,0:10:55.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,此人要敢于挑战\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}who's not afraid to challenge
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.68,0:10:57.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根深蒂固的科学范式\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}entrenched scientific paradigms.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.26,0:10:58.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,主流科学确实一直受到\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, mainstream science has always been
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.91,0:11:00.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新观点的威胁\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}threatened by new ideas.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.60,0:11:02.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错  像伽利略就因为\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}True. Like Galileo being imprisoned
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.77,0:11:04.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宣传日心说而被监禁\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}for his heliocentric model of the universe.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.73,0:11:06.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你知道塞麦尔维斯医生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And did you know Semmelweis was put in an asylum
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.66,0:11:08.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为建议医生们洗手  就被关进了精神病院吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}for suggesting that doctors wash their hands?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.83,0:11:10.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道  你知道弥贵尔·塞尔维特医生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I did. Did you know that Michael Servetus
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.72,0:11:13.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因发现了肺循环而被处以火刑吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}discovered pulmonary circulation and was burned at the stake?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.04,0:11:14.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有亨利·奥尔登伯格被逮捕...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Or Henry Oldenburg was arrested...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.18,0:11:16.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他因与其他国家的科学家通信\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Arrested as a spy for corresponding with scientists
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.02,0:11:17.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而被当做间谍逮捕\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}from other countries!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.34,0:11:19.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不是比赛好吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This isn't a competition.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.62,0:11:22.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我以为我们是在联络感情\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, I thought we were bonding.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.22,0:11:24.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧  我们就是在联络感情\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Fair enough. We're bonding.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.57,0:11:25.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你有兴趣加入我的开拓性研究\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How would you feel about joining me
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.95,0:11:27.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,寻找可能存在生命的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}in the groundbreaking search for exoplanets
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.80,0:11:28.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,系外行星吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}that could support life?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.86,0:11:29.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我非常乐意\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'd love it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.91,0:11:30.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想和我一起寻找\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How would you feel about joining me
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.94,0:11:32.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能实现时光倒流的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}in finding subatomic particles
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.38,0:11:33.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚原子粒子吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}that move backwards in time?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.57,0:11:35.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-你是指超光速粒子吗  -是的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- You mean tachyons? - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.50,0:11:37.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说什么胡话呢  赶紧开始我的研究吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's nonsense. Let's get started on my thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.03,0:11:40.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟你说一声\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You should know,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.63,0:11:43.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要用一位更有胆量的导师取代你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm replacing you with a more courageous mentor.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.65,0:11:45.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很遗憾  谢尔顿\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm sorry to hear that, Sheldon.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.63,0:11:47.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他不惧怕新观点\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}One who's not afraid of new ideas.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.54,0:11:48.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Great.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.58,0:11:49.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别想成是我离你而去了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Don't think of it as me walking away,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.91,0:11:52.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想成是你被抛下就好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}think of it as you being left behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.71,0:11:53.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不介意\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm okay with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.87,0:11:55.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感谢你一路以来对我的帮助\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thank you for helping me on my journey.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.27,0:11:56.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但你就像火箭助推器\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But you're like a rocket booster
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.46,0:11:57.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我必须丢弃你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}that must be discarded
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.24,0:11:59.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才能达到逃逸速度\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}for me to reach escape velocity.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.28,0:12:00.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明白\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.60,0:12:01.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我走了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm walking away now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.84,0:12:02.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再见\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.11,0:12:04.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我倒退着走\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm walking backwards,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.03,0:12:06.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样你的身影就会在我眼前渐渐消失\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}so it seems like you're fading into obscurity.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.18,0:12:07.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Neat.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.02,0:12:07.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,保重\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Take care.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.25,0:12:09.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Farewell.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.30,0:12:10.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜拜\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Ciao.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.51,0:12:12.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,旅途愉快\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Bon voyage.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.29,0:12:14.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回头见\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Arrivederci.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.58,0:12:19.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多么有魅力的年轻人啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What a charming young man.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.62,0:12:20.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怪咖\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Kook.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.06,0:12:23.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.92,0:12:26.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是布兰妮啊  什么事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, hi, Britney. What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.97,0:12:28.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,周六\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Saturday?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.77,0:12:31.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实我...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.21,0:12:35.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有空  谢谢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm totally free, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.37,0:12:36.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你最好了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're the best.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.27,0:12:41.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能我才是贱人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Maybe I'm the bitch.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.13,0:12:45.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你干嘛告诉医生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Why would you tell the doctor
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.53,0:12:47.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我怀孕的时候你才17岁\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I got pregnant when you were 17?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.96,0:12:49.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她问我们的交往历史嘛\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She asked what our history was.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.60,0:12:51.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她是指病史\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Medical history!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.00,0:12:52.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是她讲话有歧义啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That was unclear.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.86,0:12:59.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.69,0:13:01.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,惨了  我把钥匙反锁在车里了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This is bad. I locked the keys in the car.
